      "writtenOn": "2020-12-07T15:53:47Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Maybe something like this?\n\n  if (!bounds.isFinite() || paint.nothingToDraw()) {\n      return true;\n  }\n  SkRect storage;\n  return paint.canComputeFastBounds()\n      \u0026\u0026 canvas-\u003equickReject(paint.computeFastBounds(bounds, \u0026storage));",
