        "id": 5045
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-12-07T15:53:47Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think on balance I\u0027d still prefer an approach that passes a forced style to quick_reject(), but if we like this approach, let\u0027s go with it consistently everywhere?  This is init_fill_paint(), and there\u0027d be an equivalent init_stroke_paint()?",
      "revId": "70b0c520af88e5b162a5f23d73f19e7b4db8f513",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02"
