      "writtenOn": "2020-12-07T15:53:47Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "This feels like it might be a subtle change.  Are we sure we draw the same through paint\u003dnullptr and paint\u003ddefault SkPaint?",
      "revId": "70b0c520af88e5b162a5f23d73f19e7b4db8f513",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02"
